@node Intro "AMOS Extension Examiner - Intro"

      After spending alot of my time manually translating a bunch of
      AMOS extensions, I decided to create this program.
      It does all the hard work. It allows you to not only view a list
      of commands, but view error messages and much more. If that wasn't
      good enough, it even allows you to export some, or all, of the data
      to a textfile for easy viewing later on :)


@endnode

@node Filelist "AMOS Extension Examiner - Filelist"

